				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5159298#post-3817230</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5159298/scp-3124#post-3817230</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 29 May 2018 22:00:57 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Britefire</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3859803</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>One of my first +1's here; mostly because of the feeling of it just being an anomalous object and having a hint of older Series 1 and 2 skips because of it.</p> <p>It felt concise, just enough information to be interesting without feeling like it drags on and overstays it's welcome, and an origin that's a mix of head-scratching and somewhat mundane? Compared to others, at least.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
