					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5159298#post-3702863</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5159298/scp-3124#post-3702863</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2018 19:54:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Monkeysky</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1390998</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like the impression of the SCP universe this gives us. There's lots of SCPs created for good, or for evil, but this one is just a random neutral object made accidentally from some benign goal, which happens to break the conventional laws of reality.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
