					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5159298#post-3699775</guid>
				<title>HEY: This SCP is new, and it is NOT a football.</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5159298/scp-3124#post-3699775</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2018 18:30:54 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Communism will win</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>617958</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Image is adapted from a public domain source. The original is <a href="http://www.publicdomainpictures.net/view-image.php?image=70132&amp;picture=soccer-balls">here</a>.</p> <p>For this one, I wanted something that treads closer to &quot;bizarre object&quot; than is standard these days, while still having a more tangible narrative structure to it than that kind of SCP often does.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
